####################################################
##  Update information for NConf 1.3.0 to 1.3.1   ##
####################################################

##------------------------------------------------##
##       Changes to the NConf configuration       ##
##------------------------------------------------##

The following (optional) configuration options have been added:
- LOG_REMOTE_IP_HISTORY [1|0]

##------------------------------------------------##
##     Changes to the generated configuration     ##
##------------------------------------------------##


##------------------------------------------------##
##              Additional changes                ##
##------------------------------------------------##

Changed the pattern used to parse for SNMP TRAP services within the 
collector configuration: services ending on "*TRAP" (caps) will be removed.

####################################################
##           End of update information            ##
####################################################
